de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.examples.naa

Class Naa

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.examples.naa.Naa

  • public class Naa
extends Object
    An example Network Access Authority. Listens for handshakes at localhost:30271. The NAA uses a plain socket for testing, this cannot be used for production where TLS protection is mandatory. However to achieve TLS protection just us a Java SSL socket.
